---
title: Cal Smart Chipotle-Honey Turkey Bowls with Green Onion Rice
description: This hearty turkey bowl is full of wholesome goodness! We even snuck some spinach into the turkey mix for an added veggie boost. Pickled radishes and a sweet and spicy chipotle-honey sauce brighten each bite.
